parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Seat Belt Buckle Housing Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side seat belt buckle housing can cause the seat belt to jam, making it difficult or impossible to use, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle housing is broken
the seat belt will not extend
the seat belt will not retract
the seat belt cannot be worn.

symptoms: the seat belt will not extend
the seat belt will not retract
the seat belt cannot be worn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to not function properly, making it difficult or impossible to use, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.

the seat belt buckle is broken
the seat belt cannot be worn.
